FARKAS
v.
Van LINDEN. No. S15A0859. Supreme Court of Georgia. Oct. 5, 2015. Leonard Farkas, Albany, for appellant. Alex Joshua Kaplan, Albany, for appellee.

Opinion

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the court below is affirmed without opinion pursuant to Supreme Court Rule 59.
